### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = <paste_access_token_here>
@clientId = <paste_client_id_here>
@projectId = <paste_project_id_here>
@noteId = <paste_deliverynote_id_here>

### 1) Crear albarán de horas
# @name createHoursNote
POST {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "format": "hours",
  "client": "{{clientId}}",
  "project": "{{projectId}}",
  "workDate": "2024-06-15",
  "description": "Jornada de instalación eléctrica",
  "hours": 8,
  "workers": [
    { "name": "Juan García", "hours": 5 },
    { "name": "María López", "hours": 3 }
  ]
}

### 2) Crear albarán de materiales
# @name createMaterialNote
POST {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "format": "material",
  "client": "{{clientId}}",
  "project": "{{projectId}}",
  "workDate": "2024-06-15",
  "description": "Suministro de cemento Portland",
  "material": "Cemento Portland CEM I 42.5",
  "quantity": 50,
  "unit": "kg"
}

### 3) Listar albaranes (paginación y filtros)
GET {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote?page=1&limit=10&sort=-workDate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4) Filtrar por proyecto
GET {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote?project={{projectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5) Filtrar por formato y estado de firma
GET {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote?format=hours&signed=false
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6) Filtrar por rango de fechas
GET {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote?from=2024-01-01&to=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7) Obtener albarán concreto (con populate)
GET {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote/{{noteId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8) Descargar PDF (genera on-the-fly si no está firmado)
GET {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote/pdf/{{noteId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9) Firmar albarán (multipart/form-data con imagen de firma)
# Usa ThunderClient, Postman o la extensión REST Client con soporte de archivos binarios
# PATCH {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote/{{noteId}}/sign
# Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
# Content-Type: multipart/form-data
#
# signature = < /ruta/a/firma.png

### 10) Borrar albarán (soft delete) — solo si no está firmado
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote/{{noteId}}?soft=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11) Borrar albarán (hard delete) — solo si no está firmado
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote/{{noteId}}?soft=false
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### --- BONUS: Dashboard ---
###

### 12) Estadísticas agregadas (por mes, cliente y proyecto)
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
